Hi Team,
I observed the following issues:
1. When changing the classification type, the label is not updating properly.
    ◦ Initially, I intentionally changed the classification from *Passport* to *Other* class.
    ◦ Then, I changed it back from the *Other* class to *Passport*, but the labels did not update correctly.
2. After changing the classification type, the re-extraction process fails.
    ◦ It displays all the values as *No Value Found* for all the values.
cc : @Nithin
